write_lec_files(25.10)                                  write_lec_files(25.10)

Name
       write_lec_files

Syntax
       write_lec_files {true | false}

       Type: Boolean

       Default: true

       Specifies  whether  the  write_do_lec command should write intermediate
       files to the verification directory specified by  the  write_lec_direc-
       tory_naming_style global. If false, no files are written.

Related Information
              * write_do_lec

              * write_lec_directory_naming_style

